{"tid":818020,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人因為啲小事開始唔鍾意另一半","createTime":"2018-09-13T20:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T22:48:45.000Z","uid":27996,"like":38,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c1498e5ecbd1067dec7ca682400b1f96ff867164","tid":818020,"uid":27996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T20:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對住佢有啲煩 甚至有啲討厭<br />\n一齊得唔係好開心<br />\n明明佢冇犯咩錯<br />\n只係日常生活中雞毛蒜皮既事令我反感<br />\n因為啲小事搞到想分手<br />\n好內疚"},{"pid":"b1bf4c8bded01a5186b67edb016060909c752afe","tid":818020,"uid":17232,"like":62,"dislike":3,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T20:19:38.000Z","msg":"因為你開始唔愛佢了"},{"pid":"e0a03498cf33dd40258493ed3623cc9175b85342","tid":818020,"uid":116390,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T20:19:52.000Z","msg":"咁只係因為你唔愛佢<br />\n當你真係好愛佢個陣<br />\n佢日日打你你都食死心塌地"},{"pid":"08027858c8032ef3bcf280630cea351203952afb","tid":818020,"uid":116390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T20:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁只係因為你唔愛佢<br />\n當你真係好愛佢個陣<br />\n佢日日打你你都會死心塌地</blockquote>"},{"pid":"68f07195639767a775adee9344c00a3c80661d41","tid":818020,"uid":27996,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b1bf4c8bded01a5186b67edb016060909c752afe","tid":818020,"uid":17232,"like":62,"dislike":3,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T20:19:38.000Z","msg":"因為你開始唔愛佢了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T20:28:35.000Z","msg":"係啲小事加加埋埋令我唔愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係我唔愛佢先接受唔到啲小事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6d94a511c9824a4e9022119158536cfd178ccd","tid":818020,"uid":17232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"68f07195639767a775adee9344c00a3c80661d41","tid":818020,"uid":27996,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b1bf4c8bded01a5186b67edb016060909c752afe","tid":818020,"uid":17232,"